ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of SUZANNE GILBERT of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation as Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration Appeal Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board, effective April 15, 2024.
